Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.56,0:41:46.44,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}I was always alone, back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.19,0:41:50.44,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}I wanted to disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.90,0:41:57.86,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}In the corner of the classroom where I don't belong,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.53,0:42:04.50,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}forced to carry sins even I have no knowledge of.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.54,0:42:10.25,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}Oh how frustrating, frightening.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.29,0:42:15.26,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}This closed door...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.92,0:42:20.55,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}If I could someday gather the courage to speak to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.30,0:42:26.48,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}I would wish for you to open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.60,0:42:40.78,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}I did not realise that simply by living I became...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.12,0:42:43.29,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}...your source of happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.29,0:42:50.38,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}Thank you for showing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.38,0:42:52.88,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}Now I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.21,0:42:55.71,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}I have learned of pain,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.05,0:43:00.84,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}but also of great kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.68,0:43:04.18,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}Believing in myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.56,0:43:11.61,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}if I continue walking forward, I can break free from the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.61,0:43:19.24,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}The future depends on myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.53,0:43:34.75,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}If there is so much meaning in simply living,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.13,0:43:39.17,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}then I can do it. I can overcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.38,0:43:43.64,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}I won't lose tomorrow, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.97,0:43:48.48,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}And someday, I will tell you with a smile...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.60,0:44:01.66,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}...how wonderful it is to be alive...
