Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.88,0:01:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You damned pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.68,0:01:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.80,0:01:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Of course you did!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.43,0:01:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You groped my butt, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.06,0:01:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that look, you bastard!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.35,0:01:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Criminals like you should just shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.23,0:01:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.35,0:01:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That man groped my butt.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.23,0:01:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's definitely a repeat felon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.28,0:01:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Send him off to death row.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.65,0:01:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.57,0:01:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trash like him should just die.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.28,0:01:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.61,0:01:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll take it from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.28,0:01:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll call the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.79,0:01:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Caught red-handed, you pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.66,0:01:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what excuse you have,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.62,0:01:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's not going to work here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.00,0:01:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.96,0:01:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.25,0:01:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't molest anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.09,0:01:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.63,0:01:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.46,0:01:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.88,0:01:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My business...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.34,0:02:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is! I'm his girlfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.51,0:02:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hikaru{\fscx250}-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.89,0:02:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.27,0:02:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, he has no reason to molest anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.89,0:02:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.10,0:02:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...keep him completely satisfied!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.78,0:02:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mess with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.78,0:02:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it kind of strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.20,0:02:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that his girlfriend just happened to be here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.66,0:02:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't fool us with your lies!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.84,0:02:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You saved me back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.13,0:02:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Hikaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.43,0:02:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you hadn't shown up,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.47,0:02:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I probably would've been arrested or started a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.10,0:02:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, I would've ended up being dragged off by the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.27,0:02:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's over...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.39,0:02:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.02,0:02:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all over!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.98,0:02:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having my first kiss taken away by this blond jerk...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.27,0:02:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all over for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.90,0:03:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.20,0:03:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you take advantage of me during the confusion and do something so shameless!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.66,0:03:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You perverted blond jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.37,0:03:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just how low can you get!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.62,0:03:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taking advantage of a maiden's weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.33,0:03:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Embracing and kissing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.13,0:03:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think you can do whatever you'd like?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.88,0:03:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're the one who kissed{\fscx250}-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.25,0:03:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.25,0:03:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm sorry. It was all my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.84,0:03:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.47,0:03:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.43,0:03:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of it was your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.14,0:03:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.39,0:03:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.39,0:03:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget everything that happened today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.68,0:03:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And don't tell anyone about it, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.02,0:03:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is our secret, got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.56,0:03:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Forget about it," but it's a secret{\fscx250}-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.07,0:03:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.57,0:03:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.11,0:03:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something the matter, Juu-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.07,0:03:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.37,0:03:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Hikaru make that again?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.54,0:03:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.54,0:03:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she doing well?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.00,0:03:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.17,0:03:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something related to her that you are concerned about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.30,0:04:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.30,0:04:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.72,0:04:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hikaru really cares about you, doesn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.72,0:04:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.72,0:04:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hikaru-chan is a very good little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.59,0:04:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She loves me,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.31,0:04:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I love her as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.02,0:04:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If possible, I would also like to make a bento for her, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.49,0:04:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...whenever I step into the kitchen,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.78,0:04:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,both my mother and Hikaru-chan always end up stopping me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.58,0:04:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Love, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.88,0:04:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ame...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.24,0:04:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you reckon love is?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.01,0:04:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first two characters in the Japanese syllabary.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.97,0:04:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.39,0:04:54.89,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Juuzawa Juu-kun of Class 13, 2nd Year.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.89,0:04:58.36,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Please report to the Student Council Room immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.56,0:05:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I recall, only Juuzawa-kun was called.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.57,0:05:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uninvolved individuals should excuse themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.65,0:05:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not uninvolved.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.91,0:05:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Juu-sama and I are connected by a\Nstrong bond from our previous lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.24,0:05:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a bond so strong that even the\Nlikes of Excalibur could not sever it,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.33,0:05:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayase-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.50,0:05:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just ignore her and continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.25,0:05:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.55,0:05:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Ayase Ichiko,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.01,0:05:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ochibana-san's classmate, and the\NVice-President of the Student Council.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.02,0:05:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know why I called you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.89,0:05:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.85,0:05:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my. Even though the entire school is talking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.69,0:05:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps Ochibana-san has yet to hear of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.69,0:05:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Juuzawa-kun is suspected of having\Nmolested someone on a train yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.66,0:05:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Molested?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.99,0:05:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, to escape the situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.26,0:05:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he performed lewd acts with his girlfriend in public.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.67,0:06:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.80,0:06:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.17,0:06:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm innocent!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.96,0:06:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you claim, but do you have any proof?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.97,0:06:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.30,0:06:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Juu-sama would never molest anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.14,0:06:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you be so sure of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.43,0:06:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because he is Juuzawa Juu-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.77,0:06:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that not reason enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.27,0:06:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really something, Juuzawa-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.65,0:06:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that girl from the other day is your main squeeze,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.29,0:06:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,while Ochibana-san is your backup?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.81,0:06:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. Cut it out...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.61,0:06:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quite the popular one, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.24,0:06:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, you got along well with Satsuki Miya, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.79,0:06:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps you emit some type of pheromone that attracts those kinds of girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.00,0:06:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.75,0:06:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't give you permission to leave the room, yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.63,0:06:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.42,0:06:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you've done it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.22,0:06:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Violence towards a member of the Student Council...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.89,0:06:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was just...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.56,0:06:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was because you provoked him, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.14,0:06:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayase-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.35,0:06:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiraishi-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.69,0:07:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,President.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.27,0:07:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.40,0:07:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Shiraishi Kaori.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.57,0:07:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologise for what just happened to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.86,0:07:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayase-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.53,0:07:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that Juuzawa-kun is still here is because there was no proof, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.41,0:07:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Student Council does not act on unconfirmed rumours.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.20,0:07:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said that this morning, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.37,0:07:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.04,0:07:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand why you may feel upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.96,0:07:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But even so, violence is prohibited.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.09,0:07:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you please apologise to Ayase-san for your actions?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.06,0:07:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.77,0:07:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.85,0:07:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With that, everything is settled!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.19,0:07:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.27,0:07:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Juu-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.31,0:07:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I humbly apologise.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.52,0:07:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even while standing beside you, I could do nothing to protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.30,0:07:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing for you to worry over.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.61,0:07:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was the one who snapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.36,0:07:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although, the president saved me, didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.78,0:07:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mean Shiraishi-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.37,0:08:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only is she popular, but both teachers and students alike rely heavily on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.08,0:08:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm, I suppose that kind of person exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.17,0:08:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now I understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.71,0:08:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...why people were giving me weird looks in class.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.43,0:08:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.47,0:08:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, Juu-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.72,0:08:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.52,0:08:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.52,0:08:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is about what Ayase-san said.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.98,0:08:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is this girlfriend she spoke of?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.06,0:08:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No... Like I said, that was{\fscx250}-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.78,0:08:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My apologies, I should not have pried too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.95,0:08:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whomever Juu-sama chooses to date is not something I{\fscx250}-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.16,0:08:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.79,0:08:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we go, Juu-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.25,0:08:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.13,0:08:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Juuzawa speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.80,0:08:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello. This is the Juuzawa residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.89,0:09:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wrong number?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.31,0:09:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.03,0:09:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Juu-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.03,0:09:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Regarding the rumours, should we\Ntake some measures to negate them?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.83,0:09:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rumours usually fade away on their own, so why bother?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.75,0:09:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.87,0:09:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I have a strange feeling about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.12,0:09:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Juu-sama, are you aware...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.71,0:09:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...of the suspicious incidents that have been occurring at nearby schools?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.76,0:09:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suspicious incidents?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.88,0:09:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To put it simply,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.26,0:09:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they're malicious pranks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.97,0:09:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For example,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.26,0:09:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,thumb tacks being put in indoor shoes,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.64,0:09:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,entire contents of pencil cases snapped,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.19,0:09:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,scribbles all over people's notes,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.69,0:09:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and gym clothes hidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.86,0:09:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of them so trivial that, even if reported,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.62,0:09:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,would never be taken seriously by the police,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.20,0:10:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,yet still cause only distress to the victims involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.28,0:10:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.62,0:10:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the allegations of molestation against you are in the same vein.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.21,0:10:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think you might be reading too much into it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.96,0:10:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps I am reading too much into it,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.63,0:10:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or perhaps I am not reading enough into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.84,0:10:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Juu-sama allows it, I would like to investigate this matter further.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.10,0:10:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what will you do after your investigation?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.43,0:10:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Destroy the cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.72,0:10:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.93,0:10:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if by chance things are as you suspect,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.98,0:10:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's better just to let them be.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.77,0:10:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.44,0:10:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need any more trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.15,0:10:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it. Doing something so worthless...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.91,0:10:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hikaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.00,0:10:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.12,0:10:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.84,0:11:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's still not hot enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.39,0:11:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.76,0:11:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.06,0:11:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do it with clothes on, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.06,0:11:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do what!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.98,0:11:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sex.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.98,0:11:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my first time, but I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.61,0:11:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can do whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.15,0:11:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this situation, it would be better if I take off my underwear myself, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.86,0:11:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse do to it if you're my partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.49,0:11:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.58,0:11:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you always doing stuff like this, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.70,0:11:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to disappoint you, but I have the right to choose too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.79,0:11:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do that sort of thing with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.79,0:11:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.88,0:11:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not attractive, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.01,0:11:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't mean to imply you're not attractive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.94,0:11:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.27,0:11:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...got rejected.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.44,0:11:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His name was Ibuki-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.44,0:12:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I met him at the National Karate Competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.32,0:12:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's really strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.86,0:12:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and kind...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.87,0:12:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.62,0:12:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But when I finally gathered the courage to tell him that I liked him,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.37,0:12:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he gave me a disgusted look.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.34,0:12:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when I asked him why he was angry...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.17,0:12:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did he say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.59,0:12:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.22,0:12:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...knew all about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.64,0:12:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.31,0:12:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...kissed you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.39,0:12:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who took this picture!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.77,0:12:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.15,0:12:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But someone forwarded it to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.53,0:12:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I have this picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.95,0:12:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What!? What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.99,0:12:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you're going to use this picture to mastur{\fscx250}-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.49,0:12:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.74,0:12:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you insist, then I don't mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.67,0:12:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Hikaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.71,0:13:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to be desperate\Nenough as to seek validation from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.13,0:13:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're more than cute enough already.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.01,0:13:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fancy meeting you here, Juuzawa-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.27,0:13:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The brakes on your bicycle!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.31,0:13:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think it's related to those malicious pranks that have been occurring lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.57,0:13:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I did find it strange that my brakes were cut all of a sudden,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.40,0:13:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but blaming it on someone in particular is reading too much into it, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.41,0:13:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.20,0:13:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or perhaps it's not reading far enough into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.16,0:13:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the president of the Student Council.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.00,0:13:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must have heard a thing or two about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.17,0:13:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.50,0:13:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have similar incidents been occurring at this school?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.05,0:13:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.39,0:13:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of them, we've had to deal with tons of complaints and consultations every single day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.14,0:13:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the teachers have told us not to cause a panic,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.77,0:14:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as they're already putting all of their efforts into calming down that incident with Satsuki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.11,0:14:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds rough,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.11,0:14:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even for the Student Council President.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.70,0:14:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.53,0:14:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is probably a punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.83,0:14:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Punishment?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.33,0:14:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.58,0:14:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've killed someone before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.50,0:14:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.67,0:14:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was in middle school, there was a boy who liked me,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.80,0:14:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I was already dating another person at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.55,0:14:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, one day, he...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.80,0:14:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,..told me that he loved me much more than the other person did,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.02,0:14:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and that he was even willing to die for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.23,0:14:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was unable to stop him,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.44,0:14:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and just like that, he...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.28,0:14:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all my fault anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.16,0:14:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never giving myself any free time, allowing my grades to fall...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.58,0:14:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even this leg...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.87,0:15:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to be happy,
Dialogue: 2,0:15:00.00,0:15:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then you have to put in the effort yourself, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.59,0:15:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what kind of person is behind all of these malicious pranks,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.09,0:15:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,indiscriminately committing such acts at different schools.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.55,0:15:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are not indiscriminate acts.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.68,0:15:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather, there seems to be a pattern.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.27,0:15:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you've been investigating it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.98,0:15:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was no way to rule out the possibility that you might also be affected, Juu-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.36,0:15:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I simply did a little digging.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.19,0:15:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what's the pattern?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.53,0:15:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although this is only speculation,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.70,0:15:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it seems that they are after people who seem happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.04,0:15:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It does not matter whether they are truly happy or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.21,0:15:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The important distinction is whether they appear happy to others.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.21,0:15:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, they destroy people's happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.59,0:15:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the heck {\i1}are{\i0} these people?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.05,0:15:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do not know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.59,0:15:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I have come across several rumours.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.14,0:15:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is said that there is a group that uses social networks to coordinate obscure activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.20,0:16:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just as you suspected.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.41,0:16:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're definitely escalating their activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.16,0:16:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they keep this up,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.66,0:16:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it wouldn't surprise me if someone was killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.91,0:16:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.21,0:16:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to destroy this destruction of happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.84,0:16:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.09,0:16:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.05,0:16:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mum!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.64,0:16:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that they've accumulated enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.47,0:16:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost time to collect them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.64,0:16:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please look forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.16,0:17:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.88,0:17:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My bust is 84 cm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.55,0:17:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.80,0:17:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you kept staring at them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.34,0:17:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, my hips are 83 cm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.51,0:17:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm quite proud of my child-bearing hips!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.89,0:17:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the reason why I was staring at you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.27,0:17:24.35,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,I came here to{\fscx250}-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.27,0:17:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're meeting someone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.56,0:17:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Juuzawa Juu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.81,0:17:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.20,0:17:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The person who is waiting for you is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.61,0:17:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.12,0:17:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ame.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.04,0:17:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Kirishima Yukihime.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.17,0:17:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An easy way to remember it is:
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.84,0:17:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, the {\i1}ki{\i0}ri from my family name is like, "Come any closer and be {\i1}ki{\i0}lled, you scoundrels!"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.34,0:18:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's written like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.72,0:18:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ame!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.89,0:18:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Endou Madoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.98,0:18:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Juuzawa-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.24,0:18:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like virgins?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.69,0:18:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.52,0:18:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Incidentally, there are three virgins among us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.78,0:18:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, who could they be?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.45,0:18:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's hardly a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.32,0:18:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, Juuzawa-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.12,0:18:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,up until now, the number of times in your life you've wanted to die...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.24,0:18:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...versus the number of times you've wanted to kill someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.54,0:18:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which was higher?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.08,0:18:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand the purpose of your question.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.17,0:18:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to know what kind of person you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.01,0:18:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To see whether you're suitable for Ame, or whether you're just trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.18,0:18:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if I'm trash?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.26,0:18:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think will happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.64,0:18:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurts, Madoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.85,0:18:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bit my tongue.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.68,0:18:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough of your tomfoolery.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.69,0:18:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.44,0:18:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukihime has always been pretty extreme\Nwhen it comes to people she likes and dislikes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.07,0:19:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever she finds someone even the\Nslightest bit interesting, she likes to test them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.66,0:19:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, just to make things clear, I don't like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.46,0:19:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that is not due to anything that you personally did.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.42,0:19:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just hate men and broccoli.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.55,0:19:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how I am, so don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.05,0:19:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And one more thing, Juuzawa-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.05,0:19:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Molesters are no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.18,0:19:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.56,0:19:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have known them both since middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.31,0:19:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's mostly because we share the same interests,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.61,0:19:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but they're also very reliable friends in times like these, so I sought their help.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.70,0:19:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Times like these?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.54,0:19:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ame.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.67,0:19:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That outfit of yours...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.88,0:19:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it look strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.38,0:19:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... It's not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.72,0:20:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the terms of the exchange!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.84,0:20:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since Ame wanted our assistance, we're having her help out with this part-time job.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.60,0:20:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got a general sense of the situation from Ame.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.19,0:20:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's your turn to talk,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.56,0:20:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Juuzawa Juu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.91,0:20:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those two sure are amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.99,0:20:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were able to get a hold of her\Naddress just by calling a few numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.37,0:20:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But how exactly are we going to get in?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.25,0:20:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't answer her phone, and she's\Nprobably shut herself in with a bunch of guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.92,0:20:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention, those guys are probably a rough bunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.84,0:20:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need not worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.63,0:20:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather, you should be more concerned for those guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.40,0:20:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you people!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.28,0:21:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.40,0:21:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take your scumbag friends and get lost right this instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.37,0:21:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez! How?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.58,0:21:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know it was me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.91,0:21:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.25,0:21:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it because I didn't collect enough happiness points?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.67,0:21:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happiness points?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.67,0:21:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And because of all of the points I managed to accumulate until now,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.96,0:21:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was looking forward to the next meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.75,0:21:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.21,0:21:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happiness points, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.76,0:21:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.13,0:21:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ame?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.51,0:21:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hirose Nao-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.09,0:21:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason why your crime was exposed...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.60,0:21:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is because my happiness points exceed yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.18,0:21:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.19,0:21:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you manage that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.31,0:21:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a better way than ours?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.27,0:21:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.48,0:21:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.86,0:21:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In exchange, you will have to tell me everything you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.91,0:21:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that acceptable?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.91,0:21:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.24,0:21:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, why did you frame Juu-sama for molestation?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.75,0:21:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, you're{\ fscx250}-
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.83,0:21:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You forgot already!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.29,0:22:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just following instructions.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.88,0:22:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I accused you of being a molester and made the\Npolice take you in, I'd earn bonus happiness points.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.38,0:22:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who gave you those instructions?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.72,0:22:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuraki-san did.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.30,0:22:13.85,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,The leader of our Happiness Club, Kuraki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.23,0:22:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would never have expected them to hold the meeting at our school.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.90,0:22:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why bother gathering here?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.36,0:22:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I have some ideas, I have no solid evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.57,0:22:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be best to hear it directly from the culprits themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.74,0:22:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.87,0:22:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are the former clubrooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.62,0:22:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, they haven't been in use for quite some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.76,0:22:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody's coming out.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.31,0:22:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayase!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.43,0:22:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Juuzawa-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.48,0:23:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You... Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.98,0:23:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you're also a member of the Happiness Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.36,0:23:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's embarrassing for me to admit, but it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.07,0:23:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, I got scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.20,0:23:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll talk after.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.49,0:23:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've come to destroy this club.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.00,0:23:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry on home.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.33,0:23:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Juuzawa-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.92,0:23:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.63,0:23:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayase Ichiko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.96,0:23:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are Kuraki, the organiser of the Happiness Club, are you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.93,0:23:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about, Ochibana-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.56,0:23:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I mistaken?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.52,0:23:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If so, then why did you lock the door on your way out?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.02,0:23:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayase, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.73,0:23:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impressive, Ochibana-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.86,0:23:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have quite the number of happiness points.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.74,0:23:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.24,0:23:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.12,0:23:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the one who is controlling all of those idiots inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.75,0:24:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and the organiser of the Happiness Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.37,0:24:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.46,0:24:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you doing this!?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.63,0:24:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I wanted to be happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.51,0:24:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does that have to do with all of those malicious pranks!?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.80,0:24:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.93,0:24:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is a rather interesting point of view indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.22,0:24:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stealing other people's happiness...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.43,0:24:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...by destroying it, am I correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.15,0:24:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there exists a sum total of happiness in this world that is constant,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.73,0:24:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then your logic may hold true.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.82,0:24:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.36,0:24:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very impressive, Ochibana-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.03,0:24:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I simply voiced the most childish explanation I could think of.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.12,0:24:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.50,0:24:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I suppose it's the truth, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.84,0:24:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the process of gaining one's own happiness, one is certain to destroy the happiness of another.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.43,0:25:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm simply doing consciously what\Neveryone else is doing subconsciously.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.35,0:25:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.60,0:25:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how I became happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.69,0:25:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.94,0:25:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a pretty negative way of thinking positively.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.53,0:25:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bull!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.03,0:25:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such utter bull!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.03,0:25:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of what you guys did...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.53,0:25:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Ame!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.74,0:25:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.45,0:25:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.00,0:25:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like the trusty Three Musketeers, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.05,0:25:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps it's time to power up?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.23,0:25:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help us! Save us!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.40,0:25:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this, all of the happiness that\Neveryone has gathered is now mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.99,0:26:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ame!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.95,0:26:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood, Juu-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.84,0:26:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like I'm the happiest person, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.10,0:26:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Juuzawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.72,0:26:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.73,0:26:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Juu-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.74,0:26:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really think she won't run away?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.45,0:26:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.28,0:26:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you be sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.12,0:26:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because she believes in her own happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.12,0:26:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.00,0:26:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.50,0:26:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could ask you the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.04,0:26:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I called her here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.93,0:27:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sit anywhere you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.56,0:27:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Juu-sama, please take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.35,0:27:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It might prove useful later.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.90,0:27:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tea is fine, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.03,0:27:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.07,0:27:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.03,0:27:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I need to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.57,0:27:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the number of happiness points I have right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.54,0:27:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am able to eliminate most obstacles.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.67,0:27:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just to let you know, there's no use in reporting me to the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.50,0:27:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I left no evidence behind,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.67,0:27:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I definitely won't confess to the crime,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.59,0:27:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even if it kills me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.93,0:27:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.47,0:27:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is the mastermind behind all those malicious pranks.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.18,0:27:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is known to the group as Kuraki. There's no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.90,0:27:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuraki?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.94,0:28:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.20,0:28:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The name Kuraki comes from my divorced father.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.75,0:28:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I used to be known as Kuraki Ichiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.71,0:28:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and my brother's name was Kuraki Kazuo.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.22,0:28:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Juuzawa-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.55,0:28:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You heard from Shiraishi-senpai, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.72,0:28:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About how she once killed someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.64,0:28:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.98,0:28:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She pulls that stunt a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.40,0:28:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She reveals her secret and the trauma it inflicted on her, causing others to open up to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.57,0:28:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's good, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.78,0:28:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many people have you told your story to thus far...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.29,0:28:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.41,0:28:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.33,0:28:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not too bright, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.75,0:28:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't get it unless it's spelled out a word at a time, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.38,0:29:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The boy who committed suicide in front of Shiraishi-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.55,0:29:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is none other than your older brother, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.01,0:29:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.67,0:29:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.00,0:29:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.27,0:29:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the part about it being an unrequited affair is a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.39,0:29:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiraishi-senpai had originally been dating my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.40,0:29:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But one day, she just dumped him out of the blue,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.49,0:29:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so that she, the President of the Student Council, could go out with someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.70,0:29:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The son of a distinguished family, from a\Nlarge corporation, and with good grades...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.50,0:29:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And as such, my brother fell into despair and died...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.58,0:29:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...by cutting his own throat.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.55,0:29:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that story we just heard true?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.02,0:29:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You probably think little of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.73,0:30:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.86,0:30:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't resent you, Shiraishi-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.24,0:30:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a woman, I must applaud your practical judgement.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.91,0:30:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather, I feel like I should thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.75,0:30:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank her?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.96,0:30:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you made me realise...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.38,0:30:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...how this world works.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.92,0:30:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those few years following my brother's death were miserable.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.76,0:30:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My grandparents died.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.26,0:30:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My father got into a traffic accident, and then lost his job during a corporate downsizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.14,0:30:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My mother became neurotic from all the stress and fell ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.06,0:30:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And finally, we lost our house to arson.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.19,0:30:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My father left my ailing mother behind and disappeared,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.20,0:30:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and now my mother can't even get up from her futon.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.33,0:31:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was more than simple bad luck or misfortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.17,0:31:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was as if all of our happiness had been taken away due to my brother's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.47,0:31:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.30,0:31:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiraishi-senpai, were you unhappy?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.31,0:31:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I entered high school and saw you, I was shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.02,0:31:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You had good grades. You were the President of the Student Council, and popular, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.02,0:31:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My brother had died, yet you were blessed with so much happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.28,0:31:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While I was in an abyss of misfortune,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.66,0:31:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you were shining brightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.83,0:31:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was then that I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.42,0:31:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was as if you took up all the happiness from my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.96,0:31:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was why you were so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.72,0:31:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's an apology you want, then I'll say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.51,0:31:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that I betrayed Kazuo-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.47,0:32:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I never expected for him to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.23,0:32:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want me to apologise, then I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.52,0:32:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.11,0:32:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That won't be necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.77,0:32:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want you to return them.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.78,0:32:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mum, I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.29,0:32:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayase, that's{\fscx250}-
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.09,0:32:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.01,0:32:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see, she's not feeling too well.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.84,0:32:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems I've made a miscalculation.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.97,0:32:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like I still don't have enough happiness points yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.94,0:32:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Don't kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.15,0:32:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be like that, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.15,0:32:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.77,0:32:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want you to return them.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.04,0:33:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want you to return the happiness points you stole from my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.12,0:33:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But how can I do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.83,0:33:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.29,0:33:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just need to destroy your happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.34,0:33:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For example, you're rather pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.92,0:33:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if I cut off your ears or your nose?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.97,0:33:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or your eyes could work too.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.76,0:33:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, your breasts wouldn't be a bad choice, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.27,0:33:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.77,0:33:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you would, please go ahead and do it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.23,0:33:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.81,0:33:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.73,0:33:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.36,0:33:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just shut up and do it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.41,0:33:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you return those happiness points,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.79,0:33:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then my mother will recover.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.21,0:33:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I collect even more happiness points,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.04,0:33:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then perhaps father will come back, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.09,0:33:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan might even return from the other side, as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.80,0:33:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So do it, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.88,0:33:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.43,0:33:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. Which part do you want to cut?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.64,0:34:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.80,0:34:03.43,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Your ears?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.85,0:34:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ordinary and the unordinary are closely connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.06,0:34:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only difference is in one's perspective.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.48,0:34:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will be all right, Juu-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.44,0:34:10.98,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Or perhaps we could slice off some skin from different parts of your face?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.48,0:34:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shall not lose to something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.59,0:34:15.53,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Your finger would be fine, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.53,0:34:18.03,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,But do take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.03,0:34:20.78,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,If you die, disposing of your corpse will be troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.78,0:34:22.83,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,So please be careful, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.58,0:34:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Juu-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.58,0:34:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I beseech thee.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.16,0:34:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, give me your orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.08,0:34:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,End this.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.17,0:34:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.59,0:34:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall inflict punishment upon those foul beings.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.09,0:34:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just hurry up and do it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.88,0:34:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.51,0:34:38.72,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,You{\fscx250}-
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.13,0:34:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayase-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.26,0:34:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would like to speak with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.55,0:34:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can it wait a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.10,0:34:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm somewhat preoccupied at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.06,0:34:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is something I have been wondering about.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.77,0:34:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiraishi-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.90,0:34:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayase-san's older brother killed himself right in front of your eyes, did he not?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.90,0:34:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.28,0:35:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he was willing to die for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.45,0:35:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and he actually did.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.20,0:35:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you describe his expression at that moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.13,0:35:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.42,0:35:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was he smiling happily?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.84,0:35:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, he was smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.46,0:35:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happily...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.72,0:35:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea why, but he was smiling!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.89,0:35:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ochibana-san, what are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.22,0:35:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayase-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.56,0:35:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The person who took away the happiness points from you and your family...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.69,0:35:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...was not Shiraishi-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.35,0:35:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.23,0:35:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because when Onii-chan died...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.44,0:35:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you finally realised?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.95,0:35:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The person who took the happiness points from your family...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.12,0:35:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...was your older brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.96,0:35:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With his own death, he destroyed the happiness of your family.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.08,0:35:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the same time, he took away those happiness points.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.59,0:35:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus he died while at his happiest,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.72,0:36:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,making his happiness everlasting.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.64,0:36:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He yearned for it so much that he was willing to steal his family's happiness points to achieve it,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.39,0:36:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and he succeeded admirably.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.48,0:36:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you saying that my brother knew this truth all along?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.90,0:36:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.44,0:36:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The problem is not whether he did or did not know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.07,0:36:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"In the process of gaining one's own happiness, one is certain to destroy the happiness of another."
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.74,0:36:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is what you said, Ayase-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.17,0:36:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's cruel, Onii-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.60,0:36:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The destruction of happiness, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.39,0:36:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was she truly happy doing something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.07,0:36:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe so.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.73,0:37:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because during that time, she could convince herself...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.57,0:37:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that her ordeal would soon be over.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.99,0:37:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that just turning your back on reality?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.12,0:37:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.54,0:37:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The quickest way to achieve happiness...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.54,0:37:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is to avoid looking at reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.88,0:37:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think happiness means?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.80,0:37:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must surely be what I am feeling right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.14,0:37:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Ame.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.06,0:37:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I need to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.73,0:37:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.23,0:37:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about the girlfriend who saved me during that molestation incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.44,0:37:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not what you promised!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.28,0:37:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you have to go and tell Onee-chan, of all people!?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.99,0:37:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hikaru-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.95,0:37:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.58,0:37:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.21,0:37:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am very happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.88,0:38:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that you were able to save Juu-sama\Nfrom a crisis of which I was not even aware.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.63,0:38:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.84,0:38:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in apology, I tried to resolve your misunderstanding...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.30,0:38:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...with that Ibuki guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.68,0:38:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.52,0:38:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.68,0:38:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure this time he'll listen to you properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.35,0:38:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But how...?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.77,0:38:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Juuzawa-kun here took on Ibuki in a one-on-one battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.52,0:38:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,all for Hikaru-chan's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.69,0:38:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He stood there without returning a single blow until Ibuki gave up!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.32,0:38:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every now and then, boys do some\Npretty amazing things, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.95,0:38:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you go that far for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.87,0:38:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You saved me before, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.96,0:38:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the only reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.88,0:38:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.67,0:38:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do something misleading like that, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.05,0:38:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're giving me the wrong idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.43,0:38:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should go and watch over her.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.22,0:38:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're her sister, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.77,0:38:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.27,0:39:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if everything goes well, you can give her your blessing...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.69,0:39:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...for her happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.32,0:39:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.42,0:39:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Juuzawa-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.63,0:39:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiraishi-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.93,0:39:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was your childhood dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.56,0:39:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mine was...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.81,0:39:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.10,0:39:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I worked hard my whole life for that very reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.32,0:39:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got rid of everyone who stood in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.36,0:39:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I did to Kazuo-kun, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.20,0:39:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things were going as planned...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.58,0:40:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything was going so smoothly...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.71,0:40:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now it's all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.13,0:40:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My happiness is no longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.17,0:40:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.88,0:40:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.71,0:40:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Juuzawa-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.26,0:40:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.97,0:40:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...have a favour to ask of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.76,0:40:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give them to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.90,0:40:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see now...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.61,0:40:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You also believe in the destruction of happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.70,0:40:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ame?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.41,0:40:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard it was a traffic accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.58,0:40:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently a high school student was run over.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.79,0:40:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Juu-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.30,0:40:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Juu-sama! Juu-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.30,0:40:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Juu-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.59,0:40:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ame.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.76,0:40:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Juu-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.15,0:41:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really believe in divine retribution.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.65,0:41:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God is pretty lazy, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.24,0:41:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.03,0:41:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,every once in a while, he gets the job done.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.83,0:41:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you really can tell when I'm in danger.
